Situation on Kharg Island 'under control' following US strikes: Report






                The situation on Iran's Kharg island is "under control" and no damage to infrastructure has been found, according to Iran's Mehr News Agency.&nbsp;

The report also said that there has been no disruption to the island's oil facilities.&nbsp;

